    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-101">Rappresenta una connessione aperta a un'origine dati e viene implementata dai provider di dati .NET Framework che accedono a database relazionali.</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="74d8f-101">Represents an open connection to a data source, and is implemented by .NET Framework data providers that access relational databases.</span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-102">Il <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interfaccia consente a una classe che eredita implementare una classe di connessione, che rappresenta una sessione univoca con un'origine dati (ad esempio, una connessione di rete a un server).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-102">The <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface enables an inheriting class to implement a Connection class, which represents a unique session with a data source (for example, a network connection to a server).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-103">Per altre informazioni sulle classi di connessione, vedere [ci si connette a un'origine dati](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/connecting-to-a-data-source.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-103">For more information about Connection classes, see [Connecting to a Data Source](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/connecting-to-a-data-source.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-104">Un'applicazione non crea un'istanza di <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interfaccia direttamente, ma crea un'istanza di una classe che eredita <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-104">An application does not create an instance of the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface directly, but creates an instance of a class that inherits <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-105">Le classi che ereditano <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> deve implementare tutti i membri ereditati e in genere definisce membri aggiuntivi per aggiungere funzionalità specifiche del provider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-105">Classes that inherit <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> must implement all inherited members, and typically define additional members to add provider-specific functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-106">Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interfaccia definisce il <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection.ConnectionTimeout%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-106">For example, the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface defines the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection.ConnectionTimeout%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-107">A sua volta, il <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> classe di questa proprietà viene ereditata e definisce anche il <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection.PacketSize%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-107">In turn, the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> class inherits this property, and also defines the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection.PacketSize%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-108">L'esempio seguente crea le istanze di classi derivate <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand> e <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-108">The following example creates instances of the derived classes, <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand> and <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-109">Il <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> viene aperto e impostare come i <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.Connection%2A> per il <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-109">The <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> is opened and set as the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.Connection%2A> for the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-110">Nell'esempio viene quindi chiamato <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.ExecuteNonQuery%2A>e chiude la connessione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-110">The example then calls <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.ExecuteNonQuery%2A>, and closes the connection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74d8f-111">A tale scopo, il <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.ExecuteNonQuery%2A> viene passata una stringa di connessione e una stringa di query che è un'istruzione Transact-SQL INSERT.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74d8f-111">To accomplish this, the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.ExecuteNonQuery%2A> is passed a connection string and a query string that is a Transact-SQL INSERT statement.</span></span>  
  
